# AI Feature Patterns

When calling FastAPI from the frontend:
- Always include Authorization header with Supabase JWT
- Get the token: const { data: { session } } = await supabase.auth.getSession()
- Build URL: `${process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_FASTAPI_URL}/api/analyze`
- Always show a loading state (spinner + text like "Analyzing your resume...")
- Handle Render free tier cold start (show "This may take 10-20 seconds on first request")
- Display errors in a sonner toast
- Cache results: save fit_score, fit_analysis, generated_email to the application record

When displaying AI results:
- Fit score: large circular progress, color-coded (red <40, yellow 40-69, green 70+)
- Strengths: green checkmark icon per item
- Gaps: red X icon per item
- Suggestions: lightbulb icon per item
- Cold emails: styled email container with "Copy to Clipboard" buttons for subject and body
